{"TopicId":208444,"ForumId":38,"TopicTitle":"The never-ending word-editing experiment","CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-03T17:00:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-03T17:00:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is inspired by\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/207358-the-ever-morphing-sentence-game/page/2/#comment-4140872\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EThe Ever-Morphing Sentence Game\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe key difference here is that we start with a single word and whatever we end up with never resets.\u00A0 If it goes well, we\u0027ll end up with an entertaining short story that we all helped to write.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EYou can do \u003Cem\u003Eone \u003C/em\u003Eof the following in a single turn:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EAdd a word\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ERemove a word\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReplace or edit a word.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ECapitalisation, punctuation and the following words are free (\u003C/strong\u003Eyou can add or remove as many as are needed but don\u0027t just spam them or remove them all, obviously):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nthe\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nand\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nhe/she/it\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nis\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\na/an\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nof\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nto\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease make an effort to not dominate the story by trying to force it to say something you want it to say, and don\u0027t just make it random - the key to this kind of game is to try to work out what the\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eothers\u00A0\u003C/em\u003Eare aiming for and work along with it - to try to get on the same wavelength.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you have any suggestions for improving this experiment, please PM me or write your suggestion in a spoiler.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhoever posts first even gets to write the first word of the story. Feeling creative? Go for it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit 14 October 2022: Please\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ehighlight\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0your edit in some way so we don\u0027t need to read through the whole thing to know what was changed, thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-11-08T21:19:51Z\u0022 title=\u002211/08/2022 09:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 8, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Deddly\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Ehe/she added\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-03T19:35:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you include \u0022and\u0022 as a free word please?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-06-03T19:36:26Z\u0022 title=\u002206/03/2022 07:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EJune 3, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by ColdJ\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T05:39:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone, thanks for the suggestion\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-06-04T05:40:17Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2022 05:40  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Deddly\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T06:39:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI feel like \u0022is\u0022 should be there too.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T09:53:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a giant\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry if this seems more complicated but hopefully would make the game less so. Based on what Maria said, what if you made all connecting word of 4 letters or less free. e.g was, has , then, that, is, it, or, and, of, at, when...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-06-04T10:06:17Z\u0022 title=\u002206/04/2022 10:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EJune 4, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by ColdJ\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T12:51:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a giant rocket\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T15:29:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny rocket\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-04T16:29:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny rocket powered\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T00:53:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris\u00A0Kerman likes flies a tiny rocket powered\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cs\u003EIt seems to make sense that necessary edits to keep correct grammar when inserting/removing words should also be a free move, like I did here.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe not... I\u0027ll consider it if it is needed in the future, but in retrospect I thought of a way NOT having that as a free move could be more fun.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-06-05T00:59:04Z\u0022 title=\u002206/05/2022 12:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EJune 5, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Deddly\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T01:23:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris\u00A0Kerman likes flies a tiny lemon powered\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T06:27:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny lemon powered broom\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T07:28:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think you accidentally left a word out there, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/210882-maria-sirona/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022210882\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/210882-maria-sirona/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Maria Sirona\u003C/a\u003E. Not to worry, I\u0027ll use my turn to remove the word \u0022likes\u0022. I recommend copy \u0026amp; paste to make sure we don\u0027t miss a word or introduce typos.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222022-06-05T09:02:34Z\u0022 title=\u002206/05/2022 09:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EJune 5, 2022\u003C/time\u003E by Deddly\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EFree punctuation :)\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T10:07:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T11:22:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather than\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T12:07:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather than a rocket\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T15:57:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather than a rocket to Mars\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am going by all short connection words being free.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T16:34:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoris\u00A0Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather than a rocket to Duna\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI guess \u0022to\u0022 is ok as well. I\u0027ll add it to the list\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T16:44:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebediah Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather than a rocket to Duna\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T17:53:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebediah Kerman flies a tiny lemon-powered broom rather than a rocket to Dres\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(because everyone likes Dres)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T18:57:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebediah\u00A0Kerman flies a tiny lemon-and-soda powered broom rather than a rocket to Dres\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-05T18:59:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EJebediah\u00A0Kerman flies a tiny lemon-and-soda powered broom rather than a rocket into Dres\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Deddly","CreatedById":62955,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-06T03:16:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003EJebediah\u00A0Kerman flies a tiny lemon-and-soda powered broom rather than a rocket into Dres Canyon.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Maria Sirona","CreatedById":210882,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-06T06:34:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebediah Kerman flies a tiny lemon-and-soda powered broom rather than a rocket into a Dres asteroid\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy is it called experiment in the title\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-06T11:18:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebediah Kerman flies a tiny lemon-and-soda powered broom rather than a Comet into a Dres asteroid\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224141859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022208444\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221654497287\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210882\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Maria Sirona\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Maria Sirona said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy is it called experiment in the title\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it is a social experiment to see how the sentence evolves based on peoples inputs. I started with Boris. We could have got Natasha, or Becker, but we got Kerman because we think Kerbal here.) (Boris and Natasha were from the cartoon Rocky and Bullwinkle, Boris Becker played tennis.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CFYL","CreatedById":204552,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-06-06T11:27:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJebediah Kerman crashes a tiny lemon-and-soda powered broom rather than a Comet into a Dres asteroid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}